sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Admin
participant BadgesPage
participant BadgeApiService
participant VolunteerService
participant VolunteerRepo as VolunteerRepository
participant BadgeService
participant BadgeRepo as BadgeRepository

Admin->>+BadgesPage: Submit create badge form
BadgesPage->>+BadgeApiService: createBadge(name, description, icon)
BadgeApiService->>+VolunteerService: isAdmin(studentId)
VolunteerService->>+VolunteerRepo: isAdmin(studentId)
VolunteerRepo-->>-VolunteerService: authorized
VolunteerService-->>-BadgeApiService: authorized
BadgeApiService->>+BadgeService: createBadge(...)
BadgeService->>+BadgeRepo: createBadge(...)
BadgeRepo-->>-BadgeService: Badge
BadgeService-->>-BadgeApiService: Badge
BadgeApiService-->>-BadgesPage: Badge
